
2 NF
------

A table is in 2NF if:
-----------------------
-> It is already in 1NF ✔️
-> No partial dependency exists


Partial Dependency
---------------------
When a column depends on only part of composite primary key, not on the whole key

Key Idea
--------
All non-key columns must be depend on the Full Primary key


2NF = 1NF + Full dependency on key


